She Wasn't Supposed To Survive | Charlie Zone | Gritty Action Thriller Movie

A former street fighter is hired by a wealthy family to rescue their daughter from the life of drugs and crime in which she is trapped.  But when he succeeds he realizes the situation is not what it seemed.

2011.  Stars: Glen Gould, Amanda Crew, Cindy Sampson
